                        <div class="title line-clamp"><strong>intelligence: Intelligence in the modern era</strong></div>
                        <div class="description line-clamp">…the British, using a German <strong>Enigma</strong> encoding machine obtained from the Poles and relying on earlier decryption efforts by the Poles and the French, intercepted and deciphered top-secret German military communications throughout much of the war. In essence, the Ultra project enabled the Allies to read the mind of the…</div>
                    </a>
